com.tealium.collect.listeners

Interface PropertyUpdateListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.tealium.collect.listeners.CollectUpdateListener, java.util.EventListener, MainListener

    public interface PropertyUpdateListener
extends com.tealium.collect.listeners.CollectUpdateListener
    Implementers of this class can subscribe to Property (AKA Trait) updates by adding the listener to Tealium.Config.getEventListeners()

      • onPropertyUpdate

        void onPropertyUpdate(PropertyAttribute oldProperty,
                    PropertyAttribute newProperty)
        Indicate that a Property (AKA Trait) has changed for this visitor.
        Parameters:
        oldProperty - former trait this visitor held with the old value. If null, the newProperty was added.
        newProperty - current flag this visitor holds with the current value. If null, the newProperty was removed.
